# mk_digi - Personal Finance Tracker

## Project Overview

This is a personal finance management application for tracking budgets (50/30/20 rule), transactions, accounts, assets, liabilities, and net worth. The app uses Indian Rupee (₹) as the currency.

## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
|----------|------------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict mode) |
| Database | Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL |
| UI | shadcn/ui (new-york style), Tailwind CSS v4, Radix UI |
| State | TanStack React Query |
| Forms | React Hook Form with Zod validation |
| Auth | JWT-based with HTTP-only cookies, bcrypt |
| PWA | Serwist for service worker |
| Charts | Tremor for data visualization |

